item.title: About
item.description: Hey there! This page is included as an example. Feel free to customize it for your own use upon downloading. Carry on! Setup Some fun facts about the setup of this project include: Built for Jekyll Developed on GitHub and hosted for free on GitHub Pages Coded with Atom, an amazing code editor Designed and developed while listening to music like Ludovico Einaudi Ported to Hugo using Vim, while listening to a variety of great tracks Have questions or suggestions?
